text: Andriy Protsko (; 14 October 1947) is a former professional Soviet football forward and coach. ==References == ==External links== * * Andriy Protsko: "For me there always was main principle, to stay in football" (Андрій Процко: «Для мене завжди було головне – залишатися у футболі»).
